snippet.title: Longplay of Dr. Muto
snippet.description:
NEW AND HD VERSION: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-558CiCOqcc

Longplay of Dr. Muto, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Dec. 17th, 2002. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
